 find. I especially enjoyed the polar expeditions section, the philosophy section, and the history of evolution section. Books were one pound to four pounds each, which is incredible value for knowledge. Here\u2019s what it looked like: </p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!W8Fo!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5155b925-99af-41bf-ab96-894b958536d4_4032x3024.jpeg\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!W8Fo!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5155b925-99af-41bf-ab96-894b958536d4_4032x3024.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!W8Fo!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5155b925-99af-41bf-ab96-894b958536d4_4032x3024.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!W8Fo!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5155b925-99af-41bf-ab96-894b958536d4_4032x3024.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!W8Fo!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5155b925-99af-41bf-ab96-894b958536d4_4032x3024.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!W8Fo!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5155b925-99af-41bf-ab96-894b958536d4_4032x3024.jpeg\" width=\"1456\" height=\"1092\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/5155b925-99af-41b